n = int(input())
    a = list(map(int, input().split()))
    a.sort()
    i = 0
    j = n - 1
    count = 0
    while i < j:
        if a[i] + a[j] <= 2:
            count += 1
            i += 1
            j -= 1
        else:
            count += 1
            j -= 1
    if i == j:
        count += 1
    print(count)
